風險因素[編輯]

煙
吸菸是最容易致癌或致死的因素。吸菸增加患有肺癌，喉癌，口腔癌，食道癌，咽喉癌，膀胱癌，腎癌，肝癌，胃癌，胰腺癌，結腸癌，直腸癌，子宮頸癌和急性骨髓性白血病癌症風險。無煙菸草（例如鼻煙或嚼菸）亦增加口腔癌，食道癌和胰腺癌的患病風險。[6]
酒
It can increase your risk of cancer of the mouth, throat, oesophagus, larynx, liver and breast. The risk of cancer is much higher for those who drink alcohol and also use tobacco.[7]
肥胖
Obese individuals have an increased risk of cancers of breast, colon, rectum, endometrium, oesophagus, kidney, pancreas, and gallbladder.[8]
年齡
Advanced age is a risk factor for many cancers. The median age of cancer diagnosis is 66 years.[9]


