課程概述 Course Description
       授課內容：
1. Cancer biology : Introduction
2. Cancer biology : immunological view point
3. Esophageal cancer
4. Head and Neck Malignancy (Glioblastoma multiforme, Acoustic neuroma) 
5. Endocrine Malignancy (thyroid, parathyroid, adrenal, insulinoma)
6. Lung Cancer
7. Multidisciplinary approach for breast cancer
8. Laboratory examination and Image of tumor (CT/MRI./SPECT/Echo/ radionuclear image)
9. Hepatocellular carcinoma / Gastric cancer
10. Pancreatic cancer
11.enetic change in colorectal cancer
12.ediatric tumor- Wilm’s tumor/Neuroblastoma 
13.munotherapy for Malignancy / Metastasis treatment
14.ltidisciplinary approach for cancer trreatment (基因治療/射頻治療/微波治療/高功率聚焦超聲治療/加溫治療/冷凍治療) 
15.cologic Emergencies  (spinal cord compression syndrome, cardiac tamponade, adrenal insufficiency, hypoglycemia, tumor lysis syndrome)
16. onstructive oncology
SURGICAL ONCOLOGY    

